central Cairo, before spreading to the building next door.
</P>
<P>
Investigations are underway into the cause of the blaze, and the
security officials have ruled out foul play, Egypt's Middle East
News Agency reported. Samples have been taken from the site for
analysis to determine what might trigger the fire.
</P>
<P>
A technical committee has been formed to assess the damage in
the fire, the news agency said. 
