<HEADLINE> Cuban Boy Finally Reunited With Father (Writethru) </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
WASHINGTON, April 22 (Xinhua) -- Cuban boy Elian Gonzalez is
finally reunited with his father Juan Miguel Gonzalez at Andrews
Air Force Base outside Washington Saturday.
</P>
<P>
The U.S. federal government seized the six-year-old Cuban boy
from the home of his Miami relatives in a predawn raid, ending a
five-month standoff between the government and Elian's Miami
relatives.
