<HEADLINE> Xinhua Photo List for April 22 </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
BEIJING, April 22 (Xinhua)-- Following is the photo list for
April 22 released by Xinhua:
</P>
<P>
1. Tourists rest under a tree with some 9,000 Easter eggs in
Berlin, April 21.
</P>
<P>
2. A 27-year-old hippo gave birth to her 14th cub at Tianjin
Zoo.
</P>
<P>
3. A Mexican farmer sells his overstock of black kidney beans
in Mexico City April 21.
</P>
<P>
4. Chinese natives visit replica skeletons of dinosaurs in
Hohhot April 22 as China launches a nation-wide move of Earth Day
2000.
