<HEADLINE> Seles Enters Semifinals of Family Circle Cup </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
WASHINGTON, April 21 (Xinhua) -- Monica Seles outpowered
Ruxandra Dragomir with ease to enter the semifinals of the Family
Circle Cup in Carolina on Friday night.
</P>
<P>
Seles, third seed in the clay-court tournament, scored the
victory of 6-4, 6-1 and was to face top-seeded Mary Pierce in the
semifinals after Pierce beat Australia's Jelena Dokic 6-3, 6-1.
</P>
