<TEXT>
<P>
WASHINGTON, April 22 (Xinhua) - A Chinese naval delegation
led by Admiral Shi Yunsheng, Commander-in-Chief of the Navy of the
People's Liberation Army (PLA), wound up a seven-day visit to the
United States on Saturday.
</P>
<P>
