Yongguo, Commander-in-Chief of the South China Sea Fleet, and Rear
Admiral Zhao Xingfa, Deputy General Chief of Staff of the Navy,
arrived here on April 15 at the invitation of Admiral Jay L.
Johnson, Chief of U.S. Naval Operations.
</P>
