with Secretary of Defense William S. Cohen; General Richard B.
Myers, Vice Chairman of the Joint Chiefs of Staff; Secretary of
the Navy Richard Danzig; Admiral Jay L. Johnson, Chief of Naval
Operations; Admiral James M. Loy, Commandant of the Coast Guard;
Admiral Vern Clark, Commander-in-Chief of the Atlantic Fleet;
Admiral Dennis C. Blair, Commander-in-Chief of the Pacific Command;
Admiral Thomas B. Fargo, Commander-in-Chief of the pacific Fleet.
</P>
<P>
During the meetings, the two sides compared notes on issues of
common concern.
</P>
