<HEADLINE> Results of US vs. Honduras Match </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
WASHINGTON, April 21 (Xinhua) -- The United States defeated
Honduras 3-0 (halftime 1-0) in a Group D match of the CONCACAF
Olympic qualifying tournament in Hershey, Pennsylvania, on Friday.
</P>
