<HEADLINE> Shanghai to Host Photo Show of Italy in Chinese Eyes </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
SHANGHAI, April 22 (Xinhua) -- A photo exhibition featuring
Italy in the eyes of Chinese people will be held September 23-25
at the Shanghai Art Gallery.
</P>
<P>
The three-day show will be jointly sponsored by the Shanghai
Federation of Returned Overseas Chinese, a federation of overseas
Chinese in Italy, and a Sino-Italian exchange center.
</P>
